{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This package offers you the possibility to lock a selection of tracks including all of their items and takes. This should prevent involuntary edits to the respective tracks.\line I hope that you find this package helpful. To report any bugs, please mail to: reapack@nico-dilz.com\par}
}

